ABSTRACT
This patent specification relates to apparatus, systems, meth-
ods, and related computer program products for providing
home security/smart home objectives. More particularly,
this patent specification relates to a plurality of devices,
including intelligent, multi-sensing, network-connected
devices, that communicate with each other and/or with a
central server or a cloud-computing system to provide any of
a variety of useful home security/smart home objectives.
